title: Stylish 1BR with dramatic skyline views in the heart of Northeast!
posting_body: ['The Julia is a boutique apartment building in the heart of Northeast, at the corner of Broadway and Marshall.', "Our next door neighbors are The 1029 Bar, and we're kitty-corner from the historic Grain Belt Building and Pierre Bottineau Library.", 'Young Joni and Dangerous Man are two (!) blocks away.', "In short, the location can't be beat -- and we think our building is pretty cool, too.", '#611 -- Plan L', 'Please note, our online pricing shows the effective monthly rate when factoring in our current specials.', 'However, you would use the special up-front and pay regular market rent $1,725/mo. afterwards.', 'Unit 611 faces towards the downtown skyline.', 'With 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom, this unit has 507 square feet, and is equipped with a white quartz breakfast bar, private balcony and a large walk-in closet', '.', 'For info on amenities and to apply: <URL>', 'For your Instagram fix: @solhemcompanies', 'The Julia is managed by locally-owned Solhem Companies: <URL>', 'Prices subject to change.', 'NE Mpls -- NE -- Northeast Minneapolis -- Northeast -- Nordeast -- Arts District -- U of M -- New Construction -- Boutique -- Luxury -- Pet, Dog, Cat Friendly -- Large Dog Friendly -- Green Living -- Sustainable -- Electric Car Charging']
